title: Phish - 1994/06/16:  State Theatre - Minneapolis, MN  [SBD](FLAC
description:
For the record, 1994 was the first year that Paul Languedoc was a lot less lenient with letting those with porta-DATs connect directly to the board (hance, creating a SBD recording), so you will see that the vast majority of recordings from 1994-2000 are AUD.  Here is a rare SBD from 1994.  There are some others, really famous one, like 6/18/94 which as released officially by Phish last year (Chicago '94), and 6/11/94 Red Rocks, which was an FM broadcast.  But not too many "straight" SBDs from the years mentioned above. 


Phish
06-16-94
State Theater, Minneapolis, MN
